===Long time no see, (Trailblazer)===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Anaxa:''' Long time no see, (Trailblazer)
:'''Anaxa:''' Now, as information from beyond the sky reaches Amphoreus, a new wave of knowledge is sweeping through the students of the Grove.
:'''Anaxa:''' A student just sent me a test
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Attachment ''Which Aeon Are You?'' has been sent
:'''Anaxa:''' Have you tried it?
:{Choice} I am Akivili
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You bet, I must be Akivili
:{Choice} I am Nanook
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I am Nanook, and I hereby dub thee Lord Ravager
:{Choice} I am Aha
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm Aha, ha-men!
:'''Anaxa:''' From what I can tell, it relies on the conceptual dimensions of Paths, attempting to understand self-cognition and behavioral prediction through classification
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend Anaxa has gone offline
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend Anaxa is online
:'''Anaxa:''' I am Oroboros
:'''Anaxa:''' The comment reads:
:'''Anaxa:''' "You are not unrelated to Oroboros. Just as dromas chew on redsoil, you too are unsparing in your desire, consumption, and possession of truth. Desire is the instinct that drives your actions."
:'''Anaxa:''' "Your life motto is: Never be satisfied!"
:{Choice} Why not Nous
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Shouldn't it be the Droidhead?
:{Choice} Strangely fitting
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Strangely fitting
:{Choice} Quite gluttonous
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Quite gluttonous
:'''Anaxa:''' Kind of intriguing, but only slightly
:'''Anaxa:''' Anyway
:'''Anaxa:''' I should've assigned more homework
}}
