===Do you have any questions?===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Anaxa:''' Do you have any questions?
:{Choice} ?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' ?
::'''Anaxa:''' The user is asking questions about semiotics, so I should answer like this:
::'''Anaxa:''' The question mark, a materialization of human cognitive limitations and the gateway to all unsolved mysteries, is truly the most wonderful symbol in the world.
:{Choice} I have a question
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I have a question: Which three words can answer all questions?
::'''Anaxa:''' The user is trying to find the universal answer, so I should answer like this:
::'''Anaxa:''' I don't know.
:{Choice} I don't have any questions
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Professor, you called on me, I don't have any questions!
