::'''(Trailblazer):''' I! DON'T! KNOW!
::'''Anaxa:''' (Deep in thought...)
::'''Anaxa:''' Conclusion: The user is angry.
:'''Anaxa:''' You've reached the current question limit. The daily question segment has ended. It's testing time now.
