:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend Anaxa is online
:'''Anaxa:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Anaxa 01.png|80px]]
:'''Anaxa:''' It's you
:'''Anaxa:''' Don't worry, it's just a learning companion AI system up there
:'''Anaxa:''' So students can get their questions answered in a timely manner
:'''Anaxa:''' The language style is quite similar to my own, so the feedback has been good
:'''Anaxa:''' If you have any questions, feel free to consult the Other Me anytime, anywhere
